        "content": {
          "content_type": "text",
          "parts": [
            "Exploration:Exploitation::Divergent:Convergent::Associative:**Analytical**\n\nIn the context of cognition:  \n- **Exploration** aligns with generating new ideas or seeking novel possibilities (divergent thinking).  \n- **Exploitation** focuses on refining or applying known ideas effectively (convergent thinking).  \n- **Associative** refers to linking disparate ideas through creativity or intuition, akin to exploration/divergence.  \n- **Analytical** involves structured reasoning, logic, and narrowing down possibilities, akin to exploitation/convergence."
          ]
        },
